org.gvsig.installer.swing.api.wizard

Interface InstallerWizardPanel

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractInstallerWizard, AbstractInstallPackageWizard, DefaultInstallPackageWizard, DefaultMakePluginPackageWizard, MakePluginPackageWizard

    public interface InstallerWizardPanel
    This interface must be implemented by all the wizards. It just have a methods to manage the events that the wizard throws.
